>
> Actually, dec_preempt_count() ought to call preempt_check_resched()
> itself.  In the case of !CONFIG_PREEMPT, that call would simply optimize
> away.
> 
> Attached patch is against 2.6.0.
> 
> 	Rob Love
> 
